Gg_shiny_sandcastles
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
version 1.0 for CS:S
by Dubesinhower
release date: 12/22/08
map type: gungame

features
~~~~~~~~
no weapon spawns
up to 32 player spawns
two identical bases
elevators and ladders
hidden music! (try shooting the glass box in the middle)

copyright 2008 dubesinhower
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
if you want to edit or make corrections to any part of this map,
please contact me first at dubesinhower@gmail.com



so i made another map for gungame. this one pretty cool. it's small, and tons of fun to play. i got the idea from halo's "beaver creak", but there are a few surprises. 

there's a hidden song somewhere in the level. if you cant find it, check the readme.
